# PUBLICLY KNOWN ANVIL DEVELOPMENT ACCOUNTS.
# LOCAL CHAIN 31337 ONLY. NEVER ADD REAL VALUE OR USE ON A PUBLIC NETWORK.
# Copy to the ignored .env.local-anvil only for the opt-in local-demo profile.
# Java does not load this file; export it in the shell before starting the app.
